! --- Magnification (RED) + PIM solve basics ---
RES osdtriplet
RED -0.5
FIR
SUR SA
DEL PIM
FIR

! --- CODE V solve commands: per-family save/reload round-trip + delete ---
! Each family is exercised on its own fresh lens so the resolved solve VALUE is
! stable (coupled solves resolve to an order-dependent fixed point).  For every
! family: set via the CODE V command, SAV/RES, confirm the solve survives with
! its type + target + resolved value (curvature/thickness solves historically
! did NOT persist), then remove it with DEL SOL and confirm only osdtriplet's
! own PY image solve (S6) remains.

! PUY -- ray-slope YZ curvature solve (CUY Sk UMY j)
RES osdtriplet
CUY S3 UMY 0.1
SAV solvetest
RES solvetest
SLV ALL
DEL SOL CUY S3
SLV ALL

! APY -- aplanatic YZ curvature solve (CUY Sk AMY; takes NO value)
RES osdtriplet
CUY S2 AMY
SAV solvetest
RES solvetest
SLV ALL
DEL SOL CUY S2
SLV ALL

! PCY -- chief-ray-height thickness solve (THI Sk HCY j).  S5 is after the S3
! stop, where chief-ray solves are allowed.
RES osdtriplet
THI S5 HCY 1.5
SAV solvetest
RES solvetest
SLV ALL
DEL SOL THI S5
SLV ALL
